42 of this Code section, no amount of the tax credit shall be allowed to be carried forward to
43 apply to the taxpayer's succeeding years' tax liability.
44 (d) This Code section shall stand repealed and reserved by operation of law on
45 December 31, 2030."
46 SECTION 2.
47 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025, and shall be applicable to taxable years
48 beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
49 SECTION 3.
50 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
